Feature: An administrator should be able to add new volunteers to the system
  In order to track all the volunteers involved the project
  As a Administrator
  I want to be able to add new volunteers to the system

Scenario: Pressing add new volunteer
  Given I am on the volunteers page
  When I press "New volunteer"
  Then I should be on "volunteers/new"
  
Scenario: Adding a volunteer to the system
  Given I am on the new volunteer page
  When I fill in the following:
       | Given Name | Tyson  |
       | Surname    | Avery  |
  And I press "Submit"
  Then I should be on "volunteers"
  And I should see "Tyson Avery" within "name"
